Output assets/demo.gif

Require fzf

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Width 1200
Set Height 650
Set Padding 24
Set Margin 24
Set MarginFill "#11111b"
Set BorderRadius 12
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Set CursorBlink false
Set Framerate 30

Hide
Type `export PATH="$PWD/demo/bin:$PATH"; clear`
Enter
Show

Type "claude-accounts"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Down
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 900ms
Enter
Sleep 2200ms

Type "claude-gmail --continue"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
